<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">In respect of your request to <b>exercise your rights according to the GDPR</b>, you have the following options:</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Suppression </b>- this means your contact details and preferences are retained on our systems, but you are marked as ‘do not contact’. You will not receive any further calls or marketing from us whether or not we receive your details via any other route in the future.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Deletion </b>- this means your details are deleted from our systems and we will not have a record of you or your requirements. Consequently, as we work with a number of agencies and accountants in the contracting sector, if we were to receive your details again from another firm we may contact you in the future.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">In addition, <b>if you were already referred to us by one of these firms then they may re-send your details in the future as part of an audit</b>, especially where their contractors are required to hold insurances and Kingsbridge are their insurance compliance partner.<b> If you do not wish for your details to be re-sent to us, you will need to contact your recruiter/accountant and advise them of this.</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Please reply to this email stating whether you would like to be ‘suppressed’ or ‘deleted’.</b> If we do not hear from you we will suppress your details.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Please note that <b>you may hear from us again in the next 30 days whilst we update our systems</b> to action your wishes.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Our data fair processing notice can be accessed via the following</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">link: https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/fair-processing-notice/</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Your rights under GDPR can be accessed via the following link: https://ico.org.uk/</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">T: 01242 808 740</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>